Package api

Class EdgeData

java.lang.Object
api.EdgeData
All Implemented Interfaces:
edge_data
public class EdgeData
extends java.lang.Object
implements edge_data
EdgeData implements the edge_data interface represents the set of operations applicable on a * directional edge(src,dest) in a (directional) weighted graph.
